									<div itemprop="articleBody">
		<p>The aim of the Open Academy of International Science and Research University is to support socially related activities by focusing on the development of partnerships in the focus fields.</p>
<p><strong>Activities of the Open Academy:</strong></p>
<ul>
<li>coordination and development of continuing education,</li>
<li>offering degree study courses for the purpose of continuing education and administration of the programme “A Year in the University”</li>
<li>offering development services for organisations and coordinating development cooperation organisation of international examination</li>
</ul> 	</div>

	
